leadership_approach|results_process_vision_people|narrowing_1|1|When outcomes move faster than structure|This leadership pattern narrows when Results moves toward decisions before the work has enough structure, coordination, and repeatable standards to hold. Add Process to clarify sequence, standards, and handover before pace increases.|process|active|leadership_approach::results_process_vision_people::narrowing_1
leadership_approach|results_process_vision_people|narrowing_2|2|When productivity loses the longer view|Results and Process can make leadership look settled while the need for longer-range direction, future context, and wider meaning remains underdeveloped. Add Vision to connect the work to future context, purpose, and the reason it matters before the strongest routes define the whole response.|vision|active|leadership_approach::results_process_vision_people::narrowing_2
leadership_approach|results_process_vision_people|narrowing_3|3|When commitment is assumed too late|Even with outcomes, structure, or direction in place, this leadership pattern narrows when people are expected to align without enough communication. Add People deliberately to build trust, shared confidence, and understanding before commitment is assumed.|people|active|leadership_approach::results_process_vision_people::narrowing_3
